aggiungi al 40_custom in /etc/grub.d
__________________________________________________

menuentry "GhostBSD"{
set root=(hd2,3)
chainloader +1
}

__________________________________________________
cambia hd0,3 con la partizione/disco utilizzata

(fd0)   /dev/fd0
(hd0)   /dev/sda
(hd1)   /dev/sdb
(hd2)   /dev/sdc
__________________________________________________
